Purpose:
Handles receiving audio data (microphone from Pi) and playing it back on the laptop.

Tasks:
1. Choose audio transport method (socket or stream via HTTP/GStreamer)
2. Implement start_audio_stream() and stop_audio_stream()
3. Implement stream handler that decodes and plays audio in real time
4. Add volume/mute control
5. Buffering for lag handling (optional)

